cu.explanation_en: Setting GNB_IPV4_ADDRESS_FOR_NG_AMF to unreachable IP '10.0.0.1' will cause AMF connection failure as the CU cannot establish NGAP connection to the AMF.

du.explanation_en: Setting GNB_IPV4_ADDRESS_FOR_NG_AMF to unreachable IP '10.0.0.1' will cause AMF connection failure as the DU cannot establish NGAP connection to the AMF.
du.explanation_zh: 將 GNB_IPV4_ADDRESS_FOR_NG_AMF 設定為無法到達的 IP '10.0.0.1' 會導致 AMF 連接失敗，因為 DU 無法與 AMF 建立 NGAP 連接。
